Origin
------
Derived from the author's own `mac-operator` prototype (ai-mac-use), rebranded
and aligned to Symaira conventions. Native Swift; no third-party runtime deps.

Safety note
-----------
symaira-operate lets an AI agent control the macOS GUI (mouse, keyboard, menus,
windows). It is intended for supervised, local use over stdio MCP only — not as a
remote-control daemon. Destructive controls and secure text fields are refused
for element-based actions; passwords, payments, and permission dialogs must not
be automated without explicit user confirmation. Use at your own risk; see the
warranty disclaimer in LICENSE.
